Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.02,0:04:15.25,Kyon Sign,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(474,666)}\Nkde bych moh koupat svého psa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.56,0:04:16.70,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Jaký snob.
