Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.11,0:04:18.82,Kyon Sign,Kyou,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(467,519)}aby se svět
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.11,0:04:18.82,Kyon Sign,Kyou,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(459,537)}točil kolem mě.
